text: Tiffany Evans (born 1992/1993) is an American musician. She plays pop music and rhythm and blues. She released her first studio album in April 2008. It was called Tiffany Evans. The album was not very successful. Evans was born in New York City. ==References== Category:Singers from New York City Category:American pop musicians Category:1992 births Category:Living people
title: Tiffany Evans
